commentPreTextItems.html: 10:45: Right, bad news folks we have another wet wicket and with the experience from Friday the umpires have decided to call it off. Canada takes the series 1-0. It was great to have you here, enjoy The Ashes with our top notch team of commentators
I will see you during the U-19 Qualifiers, have a great day, this is Gary Grewal
10.32: Nothing new folks, still wet and covers are still on. The players are walking around discussing The Ashes

Welcome to King City, we have some bad news, the ground is wet, the covers are on and its overcast, not all is lost though we still might have a game may be a 30 over cruncher, stay with us for more news.
